WEBVTT

00:10:59.559 --> 00:11:01.039
Au mabawa ya maji.

00:11:01.063 --> 00:11:07.030
Fumbo la neema ni kwamba Mungu anapenda Henry Kissinger na Vladimir Putin

00:11:07.054 --> 00:11:08.213
na mimi

00:11:08.237 --> 00:11:12.593
sawa kama anavyompenda mjukuu wako mpya.

00:11:12.988 --> 00:11:14.205
Embu fikiria.

00:11:14.229 --> 00:11:16.006
(Vicheko)

00:11:16.030 --> 00:11:19.367
Harakati ya neema ndio kinachotubadilisha, hutuponya

00:11:19.391 --> 00:11:21.389
na huponya ulimwengu wetu.

00:11:21.413 --> 00:11:25.184
Kuita neema, sema, "Nisaidie,"
na kisha jiandae.

00:11:25.208 --> 00:11:27.898
Neema hukukuta wewe mahali ulipo,

00:11:27.922 --> 00:11:30.447
lakini haikuachi itakapokukuta.